a component has 4 files
    - display.component.ts
    - display.component.html
    - display.component.css
    - display.component.spec.ts


steps to ccreate a compoenent
-----------------------------
2 ways to do it
1st way
--------
    - manually create all the above specified files
    - make an entry of the component in app.module.ts
    - dont forget to use the selector of the component

2nd way
-------
    - use the command 
        ng generate component display
        or
        ng g c display
    - since we use the command we dont have to make an entry in app.module.ts file. 
        it is automatically done
    - use the selector of the component